                Corporate catering orders, birthday parties, wedding receptions, and private events bring in 3-5x more revenue per booking ‚Äî but aggregators don't capture these inquiries. You're losing lucrative opportunities.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Critical Message -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 text-center animate-in border-2 mt-12" style="border-color: var(--accent); animation-delay: 0.4s;">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
